      <![CDATA[<p>pandas笔记：</p><ol><li>过滤</li></ol><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">num_mask = df[<span class="string">&#x27;num_col&#x27;</span>]==num_val</span><br><span class="line">str_mask = df[<span class="string">&#x27;str_col&#x27;</span>]==<span class="string">&#x27;str_val&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">filtered_df = df[num_mask &amp; str_mask]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="2"><li>拼接</li></ol><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pd.concat([list1, list2, ...])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="3"><li>填充</li><li>重采样</li><li>性能优化</li></ol><p>Q:</p><ol><li>索引有啥重要作用？</li></ol><p>pandas支持两个行坐标访问方式，分别是loc和iloc，访问过滤后的df有不同的行为：<br>- df.loc[1]访问索引值为1的数据，如果某个切片没有索引值为1的数据，pandas会抛出异常。<br>- df.iloc[1]访问第2行的数据<br>2.</p><p><a href="https://xyiling.github.io/posts/eaac5978.html">https://xyiling.github.io/posts/eaac5978.html</a></p>]]>
